  </m:msub>
</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
  </m:mtd>
  </m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</equation>
</para>
<para id="element-82">
</para>
<para id="element-83">
Similarly, the tangent of the angle that vector makes with y-axis is :
